The Homeland Security Secretary called the border crisis "unsustainable."

@POTUS &amp; Congressional Dems must work with Republicans to provide border agents with the resources needed to secure our border. 

Failure to do so will continue to be devastating! https://t.co/k4EZFpo6oN

Last week, I had the honor of joining @POTUS in the Oval Office after he signed an Executive Order on safe policing.

@POTUS has taken decisive action on this issue &amp; now it is up to Congress to act. We must pass the #JUSTICEAct.

